flowchart LR
    A[GitHub Push] --> B[GitHub Actions]
    B --> C[Build Docker Image]
    C --> D[Run Tests]
    D --> E{Test Status}
    E -- Pass --> F[Push to DO Registry]
    F --> G[Deploy to Droplet]
    G --> H[Docker Compose Up]
    H --> I[Health Check /status]
    E -- Fail --> K[Rollback to Previous]